 {"id":"bd-3ar8v.6.6.27","title":"[Phase 5][Support] Seed fail-closed baseline artifacts for remediation/opportunity/sweeps integrity gates","description":"Problem: ci_full_suite_gate blocking sub-gates extension_remediation_backlog/opportunity_matrix_integrity/parameter_sweeps_integrity fail closed in offloaded runs because baseline artifacts are absent from canonical artifact paths. Scope: add machine-readable baseline artifacts at expected paths with schema-valid blocked/readiness states and deterministic source_identity fields so gates evaluate contract shape rather than missing-file skips. Validate with targeted rch tests for each gate and preflight/full_suite checkpoints.","status":"closed","priority":0,"issue_type":"task","assignee":"PinkRaven","created_at":"2026-02-17T06:22:04.806599624Z","created_by":"PinkRaven","updated_at":"2026-02-17T06:23:56.489361468Z","closed_at":"2026-02-17T06:23:56.489338585Z","close_reason":"Completed: seeded canonical baseline artifacts for remediation/opportunity/sweeps integrity gates and validated via rch preflight/full-suite gate runs","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["certification","perf-3x","phase-5","support"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-3ar8v.6.6.27","depends_on_id":"bd-3ar8v.6.6","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-17T06:22:04.806599624Z","created_by":"PinkRaven"}],"comments":[{"id":1970,"issue_id":"bd-3ar8v.6.6.27","author":"PinkRaven","text":"Added schema-valid baseline artifacts at canonical gate paths: tests/full_suite_gate/extension_remediation_backlog.json, tests/perf/reports/opportunity_matrix.json, tests/perf/reports/parameter_sweeps.json. Each artifact uses fail-closed blocked/readiness semantics with required source_identity fields so gate logic evaluates contract shape instead of missing-file skip. Validation evidence (rch): cargo test --test ci_full_suite_gate -- preflight_fast_fail --nocapture --exact (pass; only remaining blocker is practical_finish_checkpoint technical-open set), cargo test --test ci_full_suite_gate -- full_suite_gate --nocapture --exact (pass test; full-suite verdict now shows extension_remediation_backlog/opportunity_matrix/parameter_sweeps gates PASS).","created_at":"2026-02-17T06:23:46Z"}]}
